! VIE lens-drawing setting commands (NUMRAYS/DRAWSI/DRAWSF) must take effect on
! the plot.  Regression: these were rejected as unrecognized commands before
! reaching the handler that updates the plot's psm, so every replot used the
! defaults.  Now they are registered CodeV commands routed to adjustVieSettings.
RES osdtriplet
VIE
NUMRAYS 13
DRAWSI 2
DRAWSF 5
GO
